commitResults.messageTitle: Level-1, Chat Bot parrots whatever user mention except bye
Level-2, added array of strings to store user input text & display when list is entered.
Level-3. Added "mark task as done" functionality & comments. Move some code from main method to some other method.

commitResults.messageBody: Change code format to the specified java coding standard
Added 3 different task types - ToDos, Deadlines, Events through the use of A-Inheritance

Done several refactoring that move long code from the main method into a class.
Made some tweaks to the output format of the chatbot.
Added comments to some methods and class.
Created a new folder for text file containing ASCII art (text-art).

Reformatted some of the output text.
Made tiny changes to variable names.
Made changes such that the chat bot can handle description with a whitespace " ".
Removed any non-ASCII characters in the text art to prevent the runtest.bat from throwing errors.
Added test cases and expected outcome to test all the commands.
Added a copy of the text-art folder into the text-ui-test as the working directory of that is different.
All test case passed...
